# Nsit-fest A react based frontend for NSIT fests. ### Build instructions Clone the repository. Make sure you have [npm](https://www.npmjs.com/) installed; then do ``` npm install ``` Then run the start script to setup an express server and get Main.js served ``` npm start ``` ### Todo * [x] Use service worker to have the site working offline * [ ] Plan basic components required for the template * Event Calendar * Event Cards * Gallery * ... * [x] Form a repo ### Contributors | [![Divjot Singh](https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/bogas04?s=100)
